# Day 18 Scratch &mdash; Rock Paper Scissors

First, let's explore the eleventh lesson in the unit. To begin, find your ECS Version 5 curriculum and open to page 170-171.

[Access a Digital Copy of the lesson>>](http://code.org/ecs#page=170)

## Key Concepts

- Students will use all of their skills with broadcasting, variables, conditionals to complete a Rock Paper Scissors program.

## Common Difficulties

This lesson has more than one answer and students should try various approaches to solve the problem.

Students will need files: [rps .starter.sb](http://www.exploringcs.org/curriculum), [rps solution.sb](http://www.exploringcs.org/curriculum), [rps solutionb.sb](http://www.exploringcs.org/curriculum)

